/* eslint-disable sort-keys */
export const Elevation = {
    ZERO: 0 as const,
    ONE: 1 as const,
    TWO: 2 as const,
    THREE: 3 as const,
    FOUR: 4 as const,
};
export type Elevation = (typeof Elevation)[keyof typeof Elevation];
